{"tid":1279121,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Cloudflare岩岩出左初步報告","createTime":"2019-07-02T15:00:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T15:40:34.000Z","uid":10258,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"851653ea2b22abb9ece96a05582fbd25348eb7d2","tid":1279121,"uid":10258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:00:58.000Z","msg":"Cloudflare已針對此問題實施了修復，目前正在監控結果。<br />\n<br />\n描述：<br />\n重大中斷影響了全球所有Cloudflare服務。我們看到CPU出現大幅飆升，導致主系統和輔助系統崩潰。我們關閉導致CPU峰值的進程。服務在約30分鐘內恢復正常。我們現在正在調查發生的事情的根本原因。<br />\n<br />\nCloudflare has implemented a fix for this issue and is currently monitoring the results.<br />\n<br />\nDescription:<br />\nMajor outage impacted all Cloudflare services globally. We saw a massive spike in CPU that caused primary and secondary systems to fall over. We shut down the process that was causing the CPU spike. Service restored to normal within ~30 minutes. We&rsquo;re now investigating the root cause of what happened.<br />\nPosted 7 minutes ago. Jul 02, 2019 - 14:50 UTC<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cloudflarestatus.com/incidents/tx4pgxs6zxdr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cloudflarestatus.com%2Fincidents%2Ftx4pgxs6zxdr&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRcwjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=5bf08419\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cloudflarestatus.com/incidents/tx4pgxs6zxdr</a>"},{"pid":"56cc483d4a03b608f0efcd9fe72c1f65ee417326","tid":1279121,"uid":10258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:02:33.000Z","msg":"大家唔好驚住，等埋詳細報告再睇下係咪DDOS"},{"pid":"258701e392cdd10eb39679fac2f88225e6213a3d","tid":1279121,"uid":32460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:05:35.000Z","msg":"This incident affected: 全地球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"731710f4d3b9b600f937fdef9ceed6c973eba1de","tid":1279121,"uid":60434,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"reply